      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BANJO ONE STRING (8) has not raced since scoring (25.13) over 435m at Sale four months ago. Form at the trip sound including 10 wins. Drawn out but with clear running expected to go close. WHIPSTICK JORDAN (1) had been going along well winning a T3 Grade 6 three back then placing at Bendigo before missing the frame latest when fifth (24.88) at Bendigo. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. GAS LANTERN (3) showed good early burn and was there until turning but run over late to finish 6th at this track in a Grade 5. Has a good record here at this journey. The form out of her last race has been franked. One of the better chances. VINNY DEWALT (2) is a surprise last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
